node.text:
Welcome to the #HomeofBentley at #MontereyCarWeek. 

If you're coming to Monterey, make sure you visit to say hello and take plenty of Bentley pictures. 

Be sure to tag them with #BentleyAtMCW21 so that we can share your great shots with the rest of the #Bentley community around the world.

node.text:
We’re back with a #Bacalar!
 
It’s #MontereyCarWeek and we can’t wait to show you what we have planned, starting with the new Scarab #BentleyMulliner Bacalar. 

If you’re attending the event, come and see it in action this Sunday on the #PebbleConcours Concept Lawn.
 
#BentleyAtMCW21
___

This model is in a preproduction state.
